                    <h2 id="email-POSTapi-v3-user-mail-mail-delete">Delete Emails</h2>

<p>
<small class="badge badge-darkred">requires authentication</small>
</p>

<p>This endpoint allows the authenticated user to delete multiple emails by marking them as deleted.
The emails are logically deleted by setting the <code>is_delete</code> flag and <code>deleted_at</code> timestamp.</p>

<span id="example-requests-POSTapi-v3-user-mail-mail-delete">
<blockquote>Example request:</blockquote>


<div class="bash-example">
